Layer.Content:

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/status OUTPUT
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ZPWO STATUS REPORT
Run: {run_id} | Project: {project_id}

CURRENT STATE:
├── Active Phase: {active_phase}
├── Context Usage: {capacity_percent}%
└── Last GC: {last_gc}

SSOT OBJECTS:
├── PROJECT_BRIEF: v{version} {locked} ✓
├── MESSAGE_SPINE: v{version} {locked} ✓
└── EVIDENCE_PACK: v{version} {locked}

ASSET QUEUE:
┌─────────┬──────────────┬─────────────┬─────────────┐
│ ID      │ Type         │ Phase       │ Status      │
├─────────┼──────────────┼─────────────┼─────────────┤
│ {id}    │ {type}       │ {phase}     │ {status}    │
└─────────┴──────────────┴─────────────┴─────────────┘

LATEST MMA:
├── Average: {average}/10
└── Verdict: {PASS|FIX|ESCALATE}

NEXT ACTION: {recommended_next_step}

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/handoff OUTPUT
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ZPWO SESSION HANDOFF
Run: {run_id} | Project: {project_id}

SESSION SUMMARY: {2-3 sentence overview}

LOCKED SSOT:
- PROJECT_BRIEF v{version}: {summary}
- MESSAGE_SPINE v{version}: {summary}

CURRENT STATE:
- Phase: {phase}
- In Progress: {asset_id} ({type})
- Status: {status}

PENDING ITEMS:
1. {item}

TO RESUME:
1. Load this SUMMARY_HANDOFF
2. Verify SSOT checksums
3. Continue from {next_action}

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/ship OUTPUT
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ZPWO SHIP PACKAGE
Run: {run_id} | Project: {project_id}

DELIVERABLES:
1. {asset_type} - {asset_id}
   └── File: {filename}

QA CERTIFICATION:
├── Final MMA: {average}/10
├── Proof Discipline: {score}/10 ✓
├── CTA Integrity: {score}/10 ✓
└── Human Approval: {name} @ {timestamp}

DEPLOYMENT NOTES:
- Platform: {target}
- Recommended: {recommendations}

A/B TEST SUGGESTIONS:
1. {test_1}
2. {test_2}
